reviewText: It was ok.  But I would have liked some music, rather than all the talking.  B J seemed a little ill at ease.

B.J. Thomas is my favorite singer I especially like the interviews with him. I highly recommend this video profile to anyone who likes B.J. Thomas & his music. I have been a fan of B.J. Thomas ever since I heard him sing "Hooked On A Feeling & "Raindrops Keep Fallin On My Head. This DVD met all of my expectations!
